
*** TRON PROJECTS ***

This document lists all projects inside the tron repository.
For each project the following structure is shown: 

> project 

library or executable 

- dependencies

* brief description
* ...

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

> talky

libtron_talky.so		

- log4cxx

* Library defining a standard language for communication between robotic control nodes. 
* The language is divided in topics, categories and concepts.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

> tuly  

libtron_tuly.so 		

- libtron_tuly

* Utility library with multiple auxiliary classes:
* string utilities, file utilities ...
* thread utilities, brooks control utilities ...

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

> comy  

libtron_comy.so 		

- log4cxx,  libtron_tralky

* Library used for inter process communication.
* It's based on the ZeroMQ library.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

> tron_test

tron_test 		

- log4cxx + all libtron_libs

* Program used for testing all other tron projects.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


